data.description: Welcome home to 1723 Lambert Drive in Clarkston, Washington! This home offers a cozy yet spacious layout, perfect for families or anyone seeking a comfortable living space. Featuring 4 well-appointed bedrooms & 2  bathrooms. The main level has been recently revitalized w/fresh paint, adding a vibrant touch to the living spaces. The kitchen is complete with new cabinet faces equipped & soft-close doors, ensuring a seamless & quiet culinary experience. The convenience of having 3 bedrooms on the main floor cannot be overstated, offering easy access & a comfortable living arrangement. Step outside, & you'll find a private, fenced backyard, perfect for enjoying the beautiful Washington weather, gardening, or hosting gatherings. The property includes a versatile shop space.1723 Lambert Drive is more than just a house; it's a place to make lasting memories, a place to relax, & a space to grow & flourish. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!
